thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Karen McDonald

author: Karen McDonald
title: Karen McDonald
text:
Ink Station rocks!
We have been using Ink station for years; their delivery is next morning! Their after sales service is just as good!
Even though we are in a different state they recognise our on going custom, way more than any local suppliers do!
Thanks again Ink Station!
